<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53441709-the-new-climate-war"><img alt="The New Climate War: The Fight to Take Back Our Planet" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1594007301l/53441709._SX98_.jpg" />
